comment._content: Low definition monochrome image of decorated Douglas F4D-1 Skyray Bu No 139097. of “All Weather Fighter Squadron” VFAW-3. With tail code PA and ‘Modex’ nose code 12. ‘Last four’ of serial 9097 on base of rudder. Based at NAS North Island, San Diego, California. VFAW-3 was attached for a time to the North American Air Defense Command. (NORAD) Picture dated 1958. Another ‘flickr’ pic with F4D-1 139097 included, can be seen here: www.flickr.com/photos/my_public_domain_photos/4629797004/ Other low definition ‘flickr’ pictures of F4D-1 139097 may also be seen here: www.flickr.com/photos/sdasmarchives/4559218755/ www.flickr.com/photos/sdasmarchives/4559218563/ www.flickr.com/photos/sdasmarchives/4559849510/
